{"word":"κλοπή","slug":"κλοπή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κλοπή</b></el> <el>(κλοπή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλέπτω'><el>κλέπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>theft</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>furtum</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a secret act, fraud</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b>; <el>κλοπῇ</el> <i>by stealth</i> or <i>fraud</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <el>ποδοῖν κλοπὰν ἀρέσθαι</el>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> to steal away, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>the surprise</i> of a military post, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}